She pondered that. To terminate another.... even if they were a decent 
warrior. 

She nodded once, "Thy will be done, Hydras," she soft purred in a slightly 
deep voice.

Was rather interesting that Rodimus had chosen another equal ... even after 
poor little Arcee. ahhh, how she enjoyed watching her perish. & even watch 
Elita-1 perish. 

"Rodimus won't even have the chance to see her again. Functioning or 
non-functioning."

--part1_151.1fc1d36f.2c05c133_boundary
